    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7789154/" class="title-link">从《死侍》没有通过审查谈起</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7789154"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/tan-mu/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3340912-60.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/tan-mu/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">魏小河</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-02-25"
      class="main-meta">2016-02-25 16:13:16</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7789154_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  新闻报道，漫威大片《死侍》没有通过电影审查，无法在国内上映。很多漫威迷为此伤心，但是大家都识大体，非常了解没过审是什么意思，很快调整好了心态，准备用硬盘迎接这部电影。  对大多数人来说，审查制度相对遥远。这几年，电影市场空前繁荣，关于电影的讨论和报道日益增多...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/7789154/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">7有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7789154_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7789154_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



