  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7701376/" class="title-link">審查的究極進化</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7701376"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/chaima/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u3592277-9.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/chaima/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">商纸</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-12-23"
      class="main-meta">2015-12-23 14:39:40</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7701376_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  極權制度下的東歐常被作為現實的隱喻。縱然自第三波民主潮至今已有四分之一個世紀，東歐各國早已建立起資本主義制度，實現自由民主的轉型，然而，極權的陰影依然揮之不去，更隨著大國崛起而愈臻無解。 幸運的是，當年東歐高牆下的自由之聲相繼被譯作中文，進入了古老的帝國。匈...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">5有用 / 1没用</span>
